				<td colspan="2"><span>Level &gt; AA
<br />

<br />
you go on a raid and there are 5 bards standing around.  2 are 70, 1 is 65 and you at 50.  who do you think they will chose?
<br />

<br />
get over to Dulak.  great xp until 55th and the loot is hard to beat.  will make RM look like childs play for loot.  that is unless SoE has nerfed the gem drops there since gOd and OOW expansions.
<br />

<br />
only item i can reccomend is the best drum you can get your hands on.  at the time i played the best droppable drum was the TDoK.  you can find them between 4k-15k in the baz.  i also loved having my silver horn and troubadoures mace.  with those 3 instroments i seldom had to swap instroments as they are all prime/sec and that pays off big time.
<br />

<br />
there is also a voice and wind aug from LDoN camps you might want to look into.  FYI they only fit LDoN chest items too, so do loads of Nro LDoNs for the better armor.
<br />

<br />
good luck.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
